            <p><add hand="#barker">Draft for $20 to pay board bill.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><persName>Col S. F Austin</persName></p>

<p>Please pay to <persName>Mr Westall</persName> 20 dollars the amount of my Boarding.
<placeName>Brazoria </placeName><date when="1831-09-12">September the 12, 1831</date></p>

<p><persName>Edmund St John Hawkins</persName></p>
<p>[Endorsed by Austin:] Paid to <persName>Hawkins </persName>twenty dollars in cash
in addition to the within&#8212;</p>
<p><date when="1831-09-13">Septr. 13, 1831</date></p>



        </div1>
